{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-06-07T21:11:55.880Z","tool_name":"write_file","tool_id":"write_file__write_file_1780866715877_0","parameters":{"file_path":"code/README.md","content":"# Cloned Repositories\n\n1. **[martorell_grid_world](martorell_grid_world/)**\n   - URL: https://github.com/mneuronico/Grid-World-Spatial-Orientation-Task\n   - Purpose: Official code for \"From Text to Space\" (arXiv:2502.16690).\n   - Key functionality: Grid-world navigation task with different spatial information representations (SIRs).\n   - Notes: Contains probing code for LLaMA-3.1-8B.\n\n2. **[stepgame](stepgame/)**\n   - URL: https://github.com/ZhengxiangShi/StepGame\n   - Purpose: Official code and dataset generation for StepGame (AAAI 2022).\n   - Key functionality: Multi-hop spatial reasoning task.\n   - Notes: Includes the TP-MANN model.\n\n3. **[spatiallm_stepgame](spatiallm_stepgame/)**\n   - URL: https://github.com/Fangjun-Li/SpatialLM-StepGame\n   - Purpose: Rectified StepGame benchmark and hybrid reasoning solution (AAAI 2024).\n   - Key functionality: Logic-based spatial reasoning combined with LLMs.\n   - Notes: Fixes errors in the original StepGame templates.\n"}}
